lcomment EE81 block done or error: disable RIE
lcomment EE8B receive mode ($7A.7=0): store incoming byte to buffer
lcomment EEBE xfer complete: send $4A+$4B completion handshake
lcomment EEE6 verify byte count ($52 low nibble == 8)
lcomment EF07 post-block: send $7B if no error, then $77 (cleanup)
